{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "feedback-platform-collection",
		"name": "Feedback Platform - Tech Challenge Fase 4",
		"description": "Collection para testar a Plataforma de Feedback Serverless (AWS Lambda + API Gateway + DynamoDB + EventBridge + SES).\n\n## Variáveis\n- `base_url`: URL do API Gateway (alterar após deploy)\n- `feedback_id`: preenchido automaticamente após criar um feedback\n- `aws_region`: região AWS (default: us-east-1)\n- `weekly_report_function`: nome da Lambda de relatório semanal\n\n## Fluxo de teste sugerido\n1. Criar feedback com nota alta (NORMAL)\n2. Criar feedback com nota baixa (HIGH → dispara e-mail de alerta)\n3. Listar todos os feedbacks\n4. Buscar feedback por ID\n5. Forçar execução do relatório semanal",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "https://u7mylr2euc.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Prod",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "feedback_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "aws_region",
			"value": "us-east-1",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "weekly_report_function",
			"value": "feedback-platform-FeedbackWeeklyReportFunction",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Feedback CRUD",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Criar Feedback - Nota Alta (NORMAL)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201 Created', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response contém feedback criado', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.id).to.not.be.undefined;",
									"    pm.expect(json.description).to.eql('Aula excelente sobre serverless');",
									"    pm.expect(json.grade).to.eql(9);",
									"    pm.expect(json.urgency).to.eql('NORMAL');",
									"    pm.expect(json.createdAt).to.not.be.undefined;",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('feedback_id', json.id);",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"description\": \"Aula excelente sobre serverless\",\n  \"grade\": 9\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/feedback",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["feedback"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Criar Feedback - Nota Baixa (HIGH → dispara e-mail)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
