		{
			"name": "Forçar Relatório Semanal (AWS Lambda Invoke)",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Invocar Lambda Weekly Report (via AWS API)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200 OK', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Lambda executou com sucesso', function () {",
									"    // O response payload da Lambda será retornado",
									"    pm.expect(pm.response.text()).to.include('OK').or.include('NO_DATA');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						},
						{
							"listen": "prerequest",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"// NOTA: Esta request requer AWS Signature (Authorization tab → AWS Signature)",
									"// Configure AccessKey e SecretKey nas variáveis de ambiente do Postman",
									"// ou use o Postman com AWS IAM Authenticator"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "awsv4",
							"awsv4": [
								{
									"key": "region",
									"value": "{{aws_region}}",
									"type": "string"
								},
								{
									"key": "service",
									"value": "lambda",
									"type": "string"
								},
								{
									"key": "accessKey",
									"value": "{{aws_access_key}}",
									"type": "string"
								},
								{
									"key": "secretKey",
									"value": "{{aws_secret_key}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"version\": \"0\",\n  \"id\": \"manual-invoke\",\n  \"detail-type\": \"Scheduled Event\",\n  \"source\": \"aws.events\",\n  \"time\": \"2026-06-01T12:00:00Z\",\n  \"region\": \"us-east-1\",\n  \"resources\": [],\n  \"detail\": {}\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "https://lambda.{{aws_region}}.amazonaws.com/2015-03-31/functions/{{weekly_report_function}}/invocations",
							"protocol": "https",
							"host": ["lambda", "{{aws_region}}", "amazonaws", "com"],
							"path": ["2015-03-31", "functions", "{{weekly_report_function}}", "invocations"]
						},
						"description": "Invoca diretamente a Lambda de relatório semanal via AWS API.\n\n**Configuração necessária:**\n1. Na aba Authorization, selecione 'AWS Signature'\n2. Preencha AccessKey e SecretKey (ou configure nas variáveis `aws_access_key` e `aws_secret_key`)\n3. Region: us-east-1\n4. Service: lambda\n\n**Alternativa via AWS CLI:**\n```bash\naws lambda invoke \\\n  --function-name feedback-platform-FeedbackWeeklyReportFunction-XXXXX \\\n  --payload '{\"version\":\"0\",\"id\":\"manual\",\"detail-type\":\"Scheduled Event\",\"source\":\"aws.events\",\"time\":\"2026-06-01T12:00:00Z\",\"region\":\"us-east-1\",\"resources\":[],\"detail\":{}}' \\\n  --region us-east-1 \\\n  response.json\n```\n\n**NOTA:** O nome exato da função pode ser encontrado com:\n```bash\naws lambda list-functions --region us-east-1 --query \"Functions[?contains(FunctionName,'WeeklyReport')].FunctionName\"\n```"
					}
				}
			]
		}
